name: Jadevein Tea Eggs
desc: A traditional snack that is widely popular in the streets and alleys of Liyue. The flavor of the tea seeps into the egg through cracks in its shell while it is boiling, and the cracks are as beautiful as the fractured patterns of jade.

value.text: Revives a character and restores 100 HP.

customize.name: Recipe: Jadevein Tea Eggs
customize.desc: A detailed step-by-step recipe for making Jadevein Tea Eggs.

customize.name: Chenyu Adeptea
customize.desc: Tea grown in warm, moist areas in Chenyu Vale. After millennia of careful cultivation, the tea today emits a rich fragrance that can be savored from several streets away.

customize.name: Bird Egg
customize.desc: An incredibly versatile ingredient that can supply all of your daily protein needs.

customize.name: Delicious Jadevein Tea Eggs
customize.desc: A traditional Liyue snack. The aroma of tea finds itself perfectly blended into the eggs. A dollop of deliciousness whether eaten all in one go or savored in small nibbles.

customize.name: Suspicious Jadevein Tea Eggs
customize.desc: A traditional Liyue snack. It tastes no different from a standard boiled egg. Did something go wrong with the tea leaves or the cooking process?
